Text:
Ahh Used to watch this when living in NY, really good show.

Rekomenderas varmt faktiskt, mest kul att se hypade jänkare leka med vapen :P

Kollade på första idag.. Skitbra. Fortsätt med detta! TACK

Watched the first episod today. Splendid. Keep the episodes coming. Thanks a lot!!

/KUngen (The king)
Scott Helveston, who was an active soldier in this series, was killed during an ambush on his patrol in Fallujah, March 31st 2004.
